<h1>About Us</h1>

<p align="justify">
Reboot is a leading specialty foot wear retailer that caters to the foot wear needs of the entire family. 
 Reliance Footprint offers widest range of international, domestic and Reliance owned brands across men’s foot wear, women’s foot wear, 
kids foot wear, handbags, backpacks, luggage, socks, belts, wallets and shoe care.

At Reliance Footprint, we believe in the quality of our products and service which is the sole reason for our 
success. Be it indoor, outdoor, formals, casuals, sports, parties, ethnic or occasional, we offer the best 
in-trend fashion foot wear and accessories for all age groups.

Reliance Footprint operates over 200 stores across 24 states making it the leading foot wear chain in the country.

Shop at Reboot and experience unbeatable standards in quality, convenience and customer service. We aim 
to provide you the ease of shopping on the go to transform your look and keep up with the latest styles. Browse 
through our amazing collection of foot wear and accessories to transform your look and keep up with the latest styles.

You can browse through our amazing collection of foot wear and accessories, choose the products you love, ‘Share-it’ 
with your friends, order what you like, get it delivered or pick it up from the nearest store. If you are 
not sure, our “Product Advisor” will help you buy the right product or call us on 
+080 4298 1900 (MON - FRI | 9AM TO 6PM). We will provide you the latest trends, tips and 
guides through our "Wear it Right" blogs and newsletters. Connect with us on Face book, Twitter, Instagram,  or subscribe to our newsletters to stay tuned.

From high fashion labels to affordable foot wear, there’s one for everyone here at <a href="/">www.Reboot.com.</a></p>

